Terrorsaur:



Terrorsaur saw Megatron and Waspinator leave, and at a fast speed. He 
shouted after him: "Megatron! Where are you go--" Something hit his 
shoulder, nearly making him fall. He looked up, seeing Zava flying at 
him. He raised his gun arm and fired back at her.
